  "3185760": {
    "name": "Tinkerlands Demo",
    "steam_appid": 3185760,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185760/extras/36fe9226074bdb561c9eca12fbbe78e8.webp?t=1746550303\" width=600 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到造作海岛的世界！这个试玩版将带你探索程序生成的海岛，可以独自生存也可以与好友团结合作。制作强大的装备，建设你们的根据地，面对危险的敌人和头目，最终救回船长。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185760/extras/4c9a83f5e55bf920edcf40a5c0234390.webp?t=1746550303\" width=600 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185760/extras/3c8b986c157f848a17651e8996fed5a7.poster.avif?t=1746550303\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185760/extras/3c8b986c157f848a17651e8996fed5a7.webm?t=1746550303\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185760/extras/3c8b986c157f848a17651e8996fed5a7.mp4?t=1746550303\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跟你的战友一起踏上精彩的冒险之旅，一同勇敢拨开造作海岛的重重谜团。团结一致，共同发展，并肩克服一个又一个困难！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185760/extras/999d4beeaf7f8d400e11587d12fc8855.webp?t=1746550303\" width=600 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185760/extras/4aa9797fc9e094b2d3a1ec7bb279f8c4.poster.avif?t=1746550303\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185760/extras/4aa9797fc9e094b2d3a1ec7bb279f8c4.webm?t=1746550303\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185760/extras/4aa9797fc9e094b2d3a1ec7bb279f8c4.mp4?t=1746550303\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >岛上有很多东西值得探索。发现战利品，制作武器和装备，逐渐增强角色的实力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185760/extras/9e993b8e22313714043b8e24f22c8218.webp?t=1746550303\" width=600 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185760/extras/fe438c977c29f5db95de49c0b48fc1db.poster.avif?t=1746550303\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185760/extras/fe438c977c29f5db95de49c0b48fc1db.webm?t=1746550303\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185760/extras/fe438c977c29f5db95de49c0b48fc1db.mp4?t=1746550303\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >形成社群，吸纳形形色色的居民，他们不仅会与你一同生活，还会在冒险中助你一臂之力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185760/extras/807a0fe14687379ddd34e3d6e4ee1a8b.webp?t=1746550303\" width=600 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185760/extras/3681fa898225e96480da5b89c9ef6a1a.poster.avif?t=1746550303\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185760/extras/3681fa898225e96480da5b89c9ef6a1a.webm?t=1746550303\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185760/extras/3681fa898225e96480da5b89c9ef6a1a.mp4?t=1746550303\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >搜集岛屿各处的资源，消灭怪物，利用所获资源打造武器。无论威力大小，只要用得顺手就是理想选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185760/extras/639a67a0cd56bdb91cd3d9f1872d1426.webp?t=1746550303\" width=600 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185760/extras/c1b0910b783c7fb6459cb5c774630361.poster.avif?t=1746550303\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185760/extras/c1b0910b783c7fb6459cb5c774630361.webm?t=1746550303\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185760/extras/c1b0910b783c7fb6459cb5c774630361.mp4?t=1746550303\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >岛上存着魔法、古怪生物乃至违反物理学的奇特现象。让你的想象力在这里尽情飞翔吧！</p>",
